==== Clear per 64k frames ====
{{en/-}}{{en/Feature|1.1|align="right"|text=(since 1.1.0)}}

Sets the speed at which the [[Main/en/Settings/Clear frame burst|clear burst rate]] assigned to clients recovers so that new clear commands can be sent

;Valid options<nowiki>:</nowiki> [0 <= n <= 1073741824 (2**30)]
: 0: very slow
: ...
: <span style="color:blue">'''4194304: (default)'''</span>
: ...
: 1073741824: extremely fast

